
1 open c:\zkdm\ptz, in configuration file, we must write hva(Horazontal viewing angle) and vva(Vertical viewing angle) for function of mousetrace, indegrees.
such as 
hva=72.5
vva=44.8
配置若不懂,请联系曹工

2 打开cmd,进入根目录c:\zkdm\ptz,运行 install_ptz_winservice.bat

3 此时程序以windows服务的形式存在,需要你启动.详情请参考windows服务.


注:若不想利用脚本,运行cmd命令python PtzWinService.py后,会显示操作的详细提示
